Habitat.
Pelocoris bipunctulus
has been found in ponds (densely or scarcely vegetated), small lakes (densely vegetated), streams and rivers ( Roback & Nieser 1974 ; López Ruf 1989 , 1992 ; Melo & Nieser 2004 ;
Torres et al. 2007
).
